hopobject.body: Could I borrow your phone, please? abuse of prescription drugs australia Pan Shiyi, a real estate mogul, told state television broadcaster CCTV earlier this week that popular microblog users should be "more disciplined" in their postings. Last month, celebrity microblog users were called to a meeting at CCTV and warned of their "social responsibility" to protect the socialist system and the national interest, reported the People's Daily newspaper.
